---
import carousel1 from '/src/img/carousel-1.png';
import carousel2 from '/src/img/carousel-2.png';
import carousel3 from '/src/img/carousel-3.png';
import carousel4 from '/src/img/carousel-4.png';

import './TabComponent.scss';

---
  
<div class="tabs-container">
    <div class="tabs">
      <div class="tab-content active" data-tab="1">
        <h1>Combine discovery & data</h1>
        <p>Dream finds you the right prospects, or enhances your own lists with custom insights. </p>
        <p>Get the answer to any question about your targets, and enhance your outreach with those same datapoints. Easily link your CRM, so you can start messaging in moments.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tab-content" data-tab="2">
        <h1>The best email you’ve (n)ever written</h1>
        <p>We’ve built our AI sales agents to handle anything your prospects will throw at them. Whether it’s booking calls, taking product questions, or handling forwards, they keep going. </p>
        <p>When Dream first messages your prospects it’ll pick the profile that’s most likely to get a reply.</p>
        <p>Easily link your work accounts, and let them send messages as you. Or create a digital persona to mail and book on your behalf.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tab-content" data-tab="3">
        <h1>Don’t just ask questions, take action</h1>
        <p>The best teams know timing matters, and so do your AI agents. We’ve put knowledge at the heart of our product, meaning your agents, campaigns, and target lists share what they’ve learned.</p>
        <p>Your messaging is more natural, and more likely to stand out. Ask any question about your companies and Dream will find the best way to answer it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="tab-content" data-tab="4">
        <h1>Connected to the way you work</h1>
        <p>Every moment counts, which is why we’ve built Dream to connect to the tools you already use. </p>
        <p>Bring targets from your CRM, or export the data you’ve gathered back to them. Save time and respond to escalations or prospect questions directly from Slack.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-images">
      <div class="images">
        <img src={carousel1.src} alt="Image 1" class="tab-image active" data-tab="1">
        <img src={carousel2.src} alt="Image 2" class="tab-image" data-tab="2">
        <img src={carousel3.src} alt="Image 3" class="tab-image" data-tab="3">
        <img src={carousel4.src} alt="Image 4" class="tab-image" data-tab="4">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      const tabContents = document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('.tab-content');
      const tabImages = document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('.tab-image');
  
      tabContents.forEach(content => {
        content.addEventListener('click', () => {
          const tabId = content.getAttribute('data-tab');
  
          // Remove active class from all tab contents
          tabContents.forEach(cnt => cnt.classList.remove('active'));
          content.classList.add('active');
  
          // Hide all images
          tabImages.forEach(img => img.classList.remove('active'));
  
          // Show active image
          document.querySelector<HTMLElement>(`.tab-image[data-tab="${tabId}"]`)?.classList.add('active');
        });
      });
  
      // Set the first tab content as active initially
      tabContents[0].click();
    });
  </script>
  